                                        2866
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Neurocognitive and psychosomatic mechanisms of altered states of consciousness (ASC) in several Eastern traditions, such as Reiki [1], Tai chi [2], Qigong [3], Jahrei [4] and others have been studied in academic publications. For instance, the focused attention on the body (abdominal region near the navel) in yoga Tummo has been shown to increase core temperature up to "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        166,
                                        2273,
                                        1213,
                                        2866
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "38.3^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        166,
                                        2273,
                                        1213,
                                        2866
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " [5]. Authors demonstrated that a neurocognitive modeling in the form of meditative visualization in ASC is responsible for two effects: (a) increasing temperature far beyond the range of normal body temperature; (b) persistent, step- wise temperature increase long after the exercises finished. Similar effects were described in other publications [6], [7]."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 5
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        166,
                        2873,
