                                        2312,
                                        1869
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "This experimental study replicates and extends the methodologies of previous works [5], [6], [13] with practitioners of the six yogas of Naropa [15], [16] and the Dhammakaya meditation [17]. Skin surface and core temperature are measured with IR camera (wavelength "
                                },
