                                        2312,
                                        2669
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "The obtained results confirm the persistent effects reported in [5], [6], [13]. In particular, increase of body temperature up to moderate fever zone "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1262,
                                        1876,
